I know the word from REV is that the PDH is supposed to be compatible with the old Snap Action VB3 size, but after trying such a breaker and finding it to barely fit after much pushing, and even then not seem to go in all the way, I realized that the Snap Action breakers seem to have different lengths and widths than the ATO ones from REV, and maybe different thicknesses too.

The Snap Actions fit OK into the PDP.
